  "recipeInstructions": "1. Shell shrimp and halve lengthwise.\n2. In a slow cooker, combine all ingredients except shrimp and rice. Cover and cook on low for 9-10 hours.\n3. Turn the slow cooker to high and add cooked shrimp and cooked rice. Cover; cook on high for 20-30 minutes.",
